Compute coordinates for individuals

Source: R/pca.R
pca_ind_coords.Rd

Return principal component for individuals

Usage

pca_ind_coords(X, eigenvectors)

Arguments

X

X_active

eigenvectors

eigenvectors

Examples

library(FactoMineR2)

X_active <- iris[, -5] |>
  standardize_norm()

vectors <- X_active |>
  eigvectors()

X_active |>
  pca_ind_coords(vectors)
